{"tid":2273220,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"單身夏蘭特比記者取笑佢無女朋友","createTime":"2020-11-05T14:36:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T03:20:28.000Z","uid":34571,"like":42,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"69c26d60f8653d298644ef748bad5cc1b847eba2","tid":2273220,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T14:36:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2020/11/05/d/d72e26ec641cc80f94a80aa664dd30f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2020%2F11%2F05%2Fd%2Fd72e26ec641cc80f94a80aa664dd30f8.jpg&h=0aa42efc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多蒙特在歐聯中3比0擊敗布魯日，夏蘭特（Erling Haland）獨中兩元，在賽後訪談中，他卻遇到了奇怪的問題。<br />\n<br />\n  在問了一些無關痛癢的問題後，採訪者（一名CBS的記者）問道：「今晚你是一個人睡嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n  夏蘭特一愣，並回答說：「呃&hellip;&hellip;是的。」<br />\n<br />\n  奇怪的提問在繼續：「現在你不帶一個女友回家嗎，你沒有攻入帽子戲法啊。」（score除了入球，也有上手女孩的意思，記者意思是夏蘭特只進了兩球，卻沒有score到女孩，沒有湊成帽子戲法。）<br />\n<br />\n  夏蘭特看起來有些想笑，他回答：「沒score，沒有。」"},{"pid":"bfa1e1d54c15518a7ddcae1442a180261b055d38","tid":2273220,"uid":42246,"like":82,"dislike":2,"score":80,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T14:43:48.000Z","msg":"個cbs 記者都on9<br />\n佢想要女 隨時有啦<br />\n<br />\n人地成就佢投胎幾次都冇呀"},{"pid":"7ac1fc98615db7aa97f1882dfbbc060dd0c6aefa","tid":2273220,"uid":32220,"like":37,"dislike":1,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T14:44:46.000Z","msg":"佢出錢屌埋你都得啦on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa55605718558efe554078df7f4e8281bc431381","tid":2273220,"uid":34571,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"quote":{"pid":"bfa1e1d54c15518a7ddcae1442a180261b055d38","tid":2273220,"uid":42246,"like":82,"dislike":2,"score":80,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T14:43:48.000Z","msg":"個cbs 記者都on9<br />\n佢想要女 隨時有啦<br />\n<br />\n人地成就佢投胎幾次都冇呀"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T14:45:44.000Z","msg":"太樣衰唔敢溝女."},{"pid":"cc017e85f923f27c4ee23db98af3865f1dfdddfe","tid":2273220,"uid":52122,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"bfa1e1d54c15518a7ddcae